word_mean_info__list.difference: 强调客观存在的真实性，没有任何虚假。
一般用于肯定或证实对方所说的话，多承接前言，也用来加强或肯定自己说话的语气。
主要用于强调与事实或现实不相违背，也可表示不快、惊奇或某种含蓄的怀疑。
侧重于实际的事，而不是凭空想象或推测的事。

word_group.brief_definition: 患难中的朋友才是真朋友
word_group.phrase: a friend in need is a friend indeed

bilingual.source: Tolkien may indeed have been the real Father Christmas.
bilingual.target: 托尔金可能确实是真正的圣诞老人。

bilingual.source: Her analysis is right on, the problem is indeed here.
bilingual.target: 她的分析说得对，问题确实出在这里。

bilingual.source: I call things as I see them, and his performance was indeed good.
bilingual.target: 有一说一，他的表现确实不错。
他确实做了一件不寻常的事。

bilingual.source: With the pandemic, unemployment is very high indeed.
bilingual.target: 随着疫情的蔓延，失业率确实很高。

bilingual.source: It was indeed (的确) the most beautiful flower.
As in most places, those who have money live well indeed.
bilingual.target: 和大多数地方一样，有钱人确实过得很好。

bilingual.source: The parent-child relationship may indeed strengthen and mature in the process.
bilingual.target: 在这个过程中，亲子关系确实可能会加强和成熟。

bilingual.source: Indeed, predictions have been around for two decades but have not yet come to fruition.
bilingual.target: 确实，预言已经存在了20年，但还没有实现。

bilingual.source: Brynjolfsson and McAfee indeed touched on this point in their book.
bilingual.target: Brynjolfsson和McAfee确实在他们的书中谈到了这一点。

list.abstract: indeed，英 [ɪnˈdiːd]，美 [ɪnˈdiːd]。英语单词，副词。指的是确实；实在。短语搭配为“afriend in need is a friend indeed（患难中的朋友才是真朋友）”。例句为“It was indeed (的确) the most beautiful flower.（它确实是最美的花）”。 indeed近义词为just，sure。

yingyinNormal.en: Indeed, much more rational, but rather less like a ball.
yingyinNormal.zh: 确实，聊天更理性，但是跟舞会比起来就差了点。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, it is, indeed. But not in the way you imagine it. How should I imagine?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，确实脆弱，但结果并非你想象的那样。我该怎么想象？

yingyinNormal.en: Go on. They are going to combine us with York. As we knew they must. Indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 继续说。他们准备将我们和约克合并，我们一早就预料到了。确实。

yingyinNormal.en: Places without surveillance, blind spots. It also comes in digital. This will be useful indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 标注了无监控处，盲点，还有电子版本。这个确实有用。

yingyinNormal.en: And that after extensive police investigations, Richard Brook did indeed prove to be the creation of James Moriarty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 警方经深入调查证明,理查布鲁克确实是詹姆斯莫里亚蒂的假身份。

yingyinNormal.en: Kong is the Chinese word for Harbor and Hong means fragrant or picturesque and indeed before this came the metropolis it is today, it would have been very picturesque, a tiny little fishing community.
yingyinNormal.zh: "港"在中文是港口的意思，"香"的意思是芳香的或者风景如画的，确实，在香港成为如今的大都市之前，的确是一个风景如画的小小渔村。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah? Hi! Girl's night out indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的。嗨！果真是女人之夜。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yes. Indeed. Well, where is he?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是，没错，那他在哪儿。

yingyinNormal.en: This balance is very special indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个均衡的确十分特别。

yingyinNormal.en: Fine. Needy Baby, Greedy Baby indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，还真是越缺爱的小孩越贪心啊。

yingyinNormal.en: My Jane looks well, does she not? She does indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的吉英看起来不错吧，不是吗？她的确看起来很好。

yingyinNormal.en: Something serious has happened. Yes, it has. Indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 发生了一件很严重的事情，的确，的确严重。

yingyinNormal.en: So you want to set the record straight. Indeed, Dave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你想建立一个记录。是的，戴夫。

yingyinNormal.en: Indeed. Yes, sir. You nearly got Ron and me expelled.
yingyinNormal.zh: 老实说，没错。你差点害我跟荣恩被开除。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Indeed. And thanks to Galahad's recordings, we have Valentine's confession.
yingyinNormal.zh: 的确，但多亏有了加拉哈德的录音资料，我们有瓦伦丁的供述。

yingyinNormal.en: All of this implies we win the contest. Indeed, it does.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这意味着我们必须得赢得挑战才行。没错，是的。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, that was very wrong indeed, boys. Very wrong of you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是说，你们这么做实在太不对了，孩子们。简直不可原谅。

yingyinNormal.en: Indeed you're mistaken. I cannot account for this honour at all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你错了，我完全不明白你这次怎么这样看得起我们，会到这种地方来。

yingyinNormal.en: And, indeed, in our portrayal of it, we had to frankly water it down.
yingyinNormal.zh: 实际上，在我们对它的描写中，我们必须不加掩饰地把它稀释。

yingyinNormal.en: The chronosphere! Hatter! Yes indeed, Miss Kingsleigh. I've got to go back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 超时空魔球！疯帽子！没错，金斯利小姐。我必须得回去！

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
